title: Elemen - Thomson Plaza
description: 元素 is a contemporary cuisine restaurant and a subsidiary of Koufu. On the menu are a fusion of western style food like mozzarella pizza and tomato basil spaghetti, plus other food like Chinese tea tofu with wheat noodles, avocado roll. Last order is 3pm and 9pm.
streetAddress: 301 Upper Thomson Rd, Unit 01-113, Thomson Plaza
